reviewText:
An incredible linear visual novel that has you wishing that you could live on a lunar metropolis. WORLD END ECONOMiCA has one unique, distinct theme; trading on the stock market. There's some romance in the mix, as well. With around 8 hours of reading (at a decent pace) and several arcs, it leaves plenty to wonder and hope for in the next two VNs of the trilogy. Above all else, there are two key rules to remember, no matter what;

1. Never take a loss.
2. Never forget the first.

